 "remarks": "This immaculate updated colonial home features a beautifully landscaped yard and an oversized 4-car garage. The gracious living room boasts large windows and a barn door, while the formal dining room, off the kitchen, has a picturesque view. The updated kitchen is equipped with granite countertops and stainless steel appliances, leading to a breakfast room that opens to the family room. The family room includes a gas fireplace, sliders to a Trex deck, and access to a back entrance with stairs to a 5th bedroom or au-pair suite. A convenient powder room completes the first floor.  The second level hosts a stunning primary suite with vaulted ceilings, skylights, a walk-in closet and marble bath. There are three additional bedrooms, plus the 5th bedroom with a separate entrance, bath, and balcony, ideal for guests or in-laws. The lower level offers an exercise room, and the home is equipped with central air, gleaming hardwood floors, and an irrigation system. This fabulous home combines elegance and functionality.",
